/-- An equivalent expression of `Semigroup.FG` in terms of `Set.Finite` instead of `Finset`. -/
@[to_additive
/-- An equivalent expression of `AddSemigroup.FG` in terms of `Set.Finite` instead of `Finset`. -/]
